metadata.name: [ Gio's Christmas Tree ]  #1/10
metadata.description:
From my 365 challenge, where I created a unique artpiece every day of 2021. 

Wishing all the best to everyone for the holidays. Please enjoy this NFT as a gift and thank you for keeping up with my journey to Paradise. 

Finally initializing Manifold and the giving of this piece were inspired by Montreal artists, FVCKRENDER and CHROMA_CODE.
